The patent for the Slug algorithm has been dedicated to the public domain.

MoonSight uses the algorithm description and ideas for a Phase-1 host-side
outline rasterizer (apps/host-web/src/adapters/slug/; retired copy under
archive/js_glue/slug/). A future revision may port the
full band-texture GPU path to WGSL using these reference shaders.

